He
took
her
hand;
whether
she
had
not
herself
made
the
first
motion,
she
could
not
say
she
might,
perhaps,
have
rather
offered
it
but
he
took
her
hand,
pressed
it,
and
certainly
was
on
the
point
of
carrying
it
to
his
lips
when,
from
some
